OL,3,CUkrainian refugees could 'end up
OL,4,Chomeless' as welcome support phased out
OL,6,FMany Ukrainian refugees could "end up
OL,7,Fhomeless", according to a Welsh
OL,8,Fcharity.
OL,10,FMore than 7,000 Ukrainians have
OL,11,Farrived in Wales since the war began
OL,12,Fin 2022.
OL,14,FMore than two years on, thousands of
OL,15,Frefugees are now needing to find their
OL,16,Fown accommodation which is
OL,17,F"challenging" amid the ongoing housing
OL,18,Fcrisis.
