OL,3,CUkrainian refugees could 'end up
OL,4,Chomeless' as welcome support phased out
OL,6,FBecause Ukrainians were granted
OL,7,Frefugee status, they have been able to
OL,8,Fwork, access free travel and benefits.
OL,10,FIn terms of accommodation, around
OL,11,F4,000 refugees have been living with
OL,12,Fhosts and the remaining have been
OL,13,Fplaced in Welsh Government's welcome
OL,14,Fcentres - this included hotels,
OL,15,Fholiday parks and university halls.
OL,17,FBut the is now phasing out this scheme
OL,18,Fmeaning many are faced with finding
OL,19,Fnew accommodation either in the social
OL,20,For private sector.
