OL,3,CUkrainian refugees could 'end up
OL,4,Chomeless' as welcome support phased out
OL,6,FHelen McAdie is the co-founder of the
OL,7,FUkraine Solidarity Hub at Cardiff's
OL,8,FCapitol Centre. She understands it was
OL,9,Finevitable that the support would come
OL,10,Fto and end but says there are not
OL,11,Fenough housing options out there.
OL,13,FHelen said: "A lot of them are in low-
OL,14,Fskilled, low-paid work because of of
OL,15,Fthe language barrier. So to be able to
OL,16,Fafford some of the high rentals, they
OL,17,Foften have to put down six months
OL,18,Fupfront because they don't have a
OL,19,Fguarantor.
