OL,3,CUkrainian refugees could 'end up
OL,4,Chomeless' as welcome support phased out
OL,6,FThis aim is backed by the charity
OL,7,FHousing Justice Cymru, with director
OL,8,FBonnie Williams saying: "Until the
OL,9,FUkrainian situation come along not
OL,10,Fmany people realised that hosting is
OL,11,Fthing. It's actually a vital part of
OL,12,Fproviding accommodation for people
OL,13,Fseeking asylum.
OL,15,F"We still have 1,400 Ukrainians being
OL,16,Fhosted but now as that number
OL,17,Fdecreases and Ukrainians move into
OL,18,Fhousing and jobs, we need to see
OL,19,Fpeople come forward if they can to
OL,20,Fhelp us host people of other
OL,21,Fnationalities."
