OL,3,CUkrainian refugees could 'end up
OL,4,Chomeless' as welcome support phased out
OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We continue to do everything we can
OL,8,Fto help people move from short-term
OL,9,Fwelcome centres to more sustainable
OL,10,Flonger-term accommodation as quickly
OL,11,Fas possible but there is unprecedented
OL,12,Fdemand for housing.
OL,14,F"To respond to housing pressures, we
OL,15,Fintroduced the Transitional
OL,16,FAccommodation Capital Programme to
OL,17,Fhelp local authorities and registered
OL,18,Fsocial landlords quickly bring forward
OL,19,Fmore good quality longer term
OL,20,Faccommodation to support everyone in
OL,21,Fhousing need.
